snippet.title: Effie - Gameplay Scenes (PlayStation 4 and PC Game 2019)
snippet.description:
Effie is out now on PlayStation Store!

Buy on PlayStation Store: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP5642-CUSA16400_00-EFFIEUSA00000000
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/975950/Effie/

Effie is a 3D action-adventure game that combines classic elements from the genre, such as combat, platforming, and puzzles, with the exploration of an expanded world. Live a unique fantasy adventure and relive the look and feel of old-school video-games!

Website: https://effiegame.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/effiegame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/effiegame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EffieGame/
